divs: sighting detailsi was on a float trip with my friend who is 15yrs old and her mom. we went outside about 9:00pm to look at the stars and my friends mom yelled "what is that!" we saw these bright balls of light spinning over the trees. there were 4 or five of them that we could see, the tree line was in the way. the lights were yellowish\orange, hovering, and spinning very fast.
Summary: 4 to 5 yellowish/orange balls of light spinning over the trees across the street from our hotel in the distance.
